gn-up was successful Ellen van Dijkand Elisa Balsamo have both made positive steps in their training with a focus still on making the Paris Olympic Games after sustaining injuries in June and May respectively.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 378, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ellen_DeGeneres_Show\", \"score\": 0.999995556482513, \"rank\": 3.2963045488805514e-06, \"text\": \"Ellen\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ellen_DeGeneres_Show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Ellen_DeGeneres_Show\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your newsletter sign-up\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"positive steps\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"their training\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"a focus\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutchwoman is still on the mend fromfracturing her ankle in a training crash,jumping into training at home with a cast on her right foot after undergoing a successful surgery.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Dutchwoman\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the mend\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"her ankle\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"a training crash\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"a cast\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"her right foot\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful surgery\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But on reflection, the experienced Van Dijk has called it a \\\"miracle\\\" that she wasn't more severely injured.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reflection\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"the experienced Van Dijk\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"miracle\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest, the last two weeks have not been easy for me.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last two weeks\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the 3rd of June, I crashed during a training ride on my TT bike.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.9999284218222536, \"rank\": 7.155570192463758e-05, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 3rd\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"a training ride\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hit a small trailer at full speed.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small trailer\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"full speed\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After all, the only serious injury was my broken ankle,\\\" said Van Dijk in anInstagram post.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only serious injury\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"my broken ankle\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Dijk\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"anInstagram post\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was actually a small miracle, it could have been so much worse.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small miracle\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I needed surgery and I could not ride my bike for a while.\\\"\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"surgery\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"my bike\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Dijk has 37 days to get back to fitness for theParis Olympicstime trial on July 27 but she's going to give everything to try and add an Olympic Gold Medal to her illustrious palmares.\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van Dijk\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"37 days\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicstime trial\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Gold Medal\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"her illustrious palmares\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's no certainty whether the 37-year-old will make the start but she's hoping to use the lessons learned from returning to form after giving birth to her first child to her advantage.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no certainty\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"the lessons\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"her first child\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"her advantage\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1623}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In my mind, it is certainly possible.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I can not train fully yet.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will not know for sure until about three weeks from now.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about three weeks\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I saw during my pregnancy how quickly everything came back.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my pregnancy\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a completely different situation, but I gain a lot of hope and confidence from it,\\\" Van Dijk told theIn Het Wielpodcast.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a completely different situation\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Dijk\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"theIn Het Wielpodcast\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know yet whether my dream is shattered.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have already decided: this is the biggest challenge in my career.\\\"\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest challenge\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest race content\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"reviews\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"expert buying guides\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My only focus is to recover as quickly as possible and get back to standard as quickly as possible.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My only focus\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, it's not ideal, but the situation is what it is.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just trying to get to Paris in the best possible way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2357, \"end\": 2362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998981366, \"rank\": 1.0198167173232253e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best possible way\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Dijk's Lidl-Trek trade teammate Balsamo has similarly made a positive turn in her approach to the Olympics, with a return to racing possible at the Italian national championships road race this Saturday, June 22 according toLa Gazzetta dello Sport.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2427, \"end\": 2434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e1lsamo\", \"score\": 0.876375122017715, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Balsamo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e1lsamo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B\\u00e1lsamo\"}, {\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.7060867702692458, \"rank\": 0.4162